The Amiga version of ''Bombuzal'' was included as a fully working game on the [[Covermount|cover disk]] of the first issue of ''[[Amiga Power]]''.

The Super Famicom incarnation of the game was later scheduled for release on the [[Nintendo Switch Online|Online service]] for the [[Nintendo Switch]] console in July 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2021-07-21-nintendo-switch-onlines-next-three-snes-games-revealed|title = Nintendo Switch Online's next three SNES games revealed| website=[[Eurogamer]] |date = 28 July 2021}}</ref>

